<aura:documentation>
	<aura:description>
    	<p>The Automation component is used to display the automatic configuration wizard for the Marketing Cloud Connect package.</p>
        <p><b>Style considerations:</b></p>
        <ul>
        	<li>The Automation component extends the BaseComponent, so it uses the main spinner and the loadingMC class for the aura:waiting event.</li>
            <li>The Automation component has a separate modal window that can be styled using the .modal2, .modal-dialog2, .modal-content2, .modal-header2, .modal-body2 and .modal-footer2 classes</li>
        </ul>
    </aura:description>
</aura:documentation>